Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:33.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}垂著肩的你現在在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:38.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}試著閉眼感受
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:43.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}放學後的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.18,0:22:48.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}是兩人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}直到天黑所做的種種
